                        Food Allergens Web Application
                      </button>
                        <div class="description more">
                            Utilized NLTK and OCR technology to gather resturant foods and identify common and hidden allergens. Written using the Ruby on Rails Framework. Received a $4,500 research grant under The Division of Natural Sciences at Colgate for this project.
                        </div>
                      <button class="set btn btn-link moreBtn" type="button" onclick="show_more()">
                         Hamilton Central PTO Web Application
                      </button>
                        <div class="description more">
